    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a well-maintained example that strikes a perfect balance between daily utility and pride of ownership. The exterior paint still holds a deep, impressive luster, though a thorough walk-around reveals minor stone chipping on the hood and a small scuff on the rear plastic trim consistent with careful use. Inside, the cabin remains a highlight; the upholstery is clean and free of odors, with only light creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster and no tears or thinning. All interior electronics, including the infotainment system and heated seats, are fully operational. Mechanically, the car is robust. It has been serviced at regular intervals, with a recent brake pad replacement and a fresh set of tires installed less than 2,000 miles ago. The engine idles quietly and the transmission shifts seamlessly through all gears. This is a dependable, honest car ready for its next owner to drive away with confidence.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
